    "In this task, we employ MTCNN to obtain the bounding box for faces and use a Resnet pretrained with vggface2 to complete the classification tasks.",
    "[43] Celebrity-aware image captioningCelebrity-aware image captioning problem combines both image captioning and face recognition.",
